\">161</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/184_AC\" title=\"184 AC\">184</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/196_AC\" title=\"196 AC\">196</a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr></tbody></table><div>\n</div></td></tr><tr style=\"height:2px\"><td></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"width:100%;padding:0px;;;\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n</div><table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"nowraplinks collapsible uncollapsed navbox-subgroup\" style=\"border-spacing:0;width:100%;;;;\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"col\" style=\";\" class=\"navbox-title\" colspan=\"2\"><span style=\"float:left;width:6em;\">&#160;</span><div class=\"\" style=\"font-size:110%;\">\nThird century since Aegon's Conquest</div></th></tr><tr style=\"height:2px;\"><td></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"width:100%;padding:0px;;;\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">209</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/211_AC\" title=\"211 AC\">211</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/212_AC\" title=\"212 AC\">212</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/219_AC\" title=\"219 AC\">219</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/233_AC\" title=\"233 AC\">233</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/236_AC\" title=\"236 AC\">236</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/259_AC\" title=\"259 AC\">259</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/260_AC\" title=\"260 AC\">260</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/261_AC\" title=\"261 AC\">261</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/262_AC\" title=\"262 AC\">262</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/280_AC\" title=\"280 AC\">280</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/281_AC\" title=\"281 AC\">281</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/282_AC\" title=\"282 AC\">282</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/283_AC\" title=\"283 AC\">283</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/284_AC\" title=\"284 AC\">284</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/285_AC\" title=\"285 AC\">285</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/289_AC\" title=\"289 AC\">289</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/290_AC\" title=\"290 AC\">290</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/295_AC\" title=\"295 AC\">295</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/297_AC\" title=\"297 AC\">297</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/298_AC\" title=\"298 AC\">298</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/299_AC\" title=\"299 AC\">299</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/300_AC\" title=\"300 AC\">300</a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr></tbody></table><div>\n</div></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<dl><dd><i>The events depicted in <a href=\"/index.php/The_Hedge_Knight\" title=\"The Hedge Knight\">The Hedge Knight</a> take place in 209 AC.</i></dd></dl>\n<p><b>Year 209 After the Conquest</b> (<b>209 AC</b>) is a year in the <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">Westerosi calendar</a>, the 209th after <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon I Targaryen\">Aegon</a>'s crowning in <a href=\"/index.php/Oldtown\" title=\"Oldtown\">Oldtown</a> that maesters and educated people use as a reference to date the years.\n</p><p>In 209 AC Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Baelor_Targaryen_(son_of_Daeron_II)\" title=\"Baelor Targaryen (son of Daeron II)\">Baelor Targaryen</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/Hand_of_the_King\" title=\"Hand of the King\">Hand of the King</a>, died during a <a href=\"/index.php/Ashford_tourney\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Ashford tourney\">tourney</a> at <a href=\"/index.php/Ashford\" title=\"Ashford\">Ashford</a>. Later that year the <a href=\"/index.php/Great_Spring_Sickness\" title=\"Great Spring Sickness\">Great Spring Sickness</a> began, which killed tens of thousands, including Baelor's father King <a href=\"/index.php/Daeron_II_Targaryen\" title=\"Daeron II Targaryen\">Daeron II Targaryen</a>, as well as Baelor's two sons and King Daeron's direct heirs, Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Valarr_Targaryen\" title=\"Valarr Targaryen\">Valarr</a> and Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Matarys_Targaryen\" title=\"Matarys Targaryen\">Matarys Targaryen</a>. Daeron's second son, Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Aerys_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Aerys I Targaryen\">Aerys Targaryen</a>, was crowned as King Aerys I Targaryen, being the next male in line.\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:212px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Egg_Dunk_and_Sweetfoot.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/6b/Egg_Dunk_and_Sweetfoot.jpg/210px-Egg_Dunk_and_Sweetfoot.jpg\" width=\"210\" height=\"345\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/6/6b/Egg_Dunk_and_Sweetfoot.jpg/315px-Egg_Dunk_and_Sweetfoot.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/6/6b/Egg_Dunk_and_Sweetfoot.jpg/420px-Egg_Dunk_and_Sweetfoot.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Egg_Dunk_and_Sweetfoot.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div><a href=\"/index.php/Duncan_the_Tall\" title=\"Duncan the Tall\">Duncan the Tall</a> and his squire \"<a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_V_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon V Targaryen\">Egg</a>\" at the <a href=\"/index.php/Tourney_of_Ashford\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Tourney of Ashford\">Tourney of Ashford</a>, as depicted by Ted Nasmith.</div></div></div>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Events</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Births\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Births</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Deaths\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Deaths</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Events\">Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=209_AC&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li>A <a href=\"/index.php/Ashford_tourney\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Ashford tourney\">tourney</a> takes place at <a href=\"/index.php/Ashford\" title=\"Ashford\">Ashford</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rthk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rthk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>The minor branch of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Fossoway_of_New_Barrel\" title=\"House Fossoway of New Barrel\">House Fossoway</a> (aka \"the green-apple Fossoways\") is founded.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rthk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rthk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Aerion_Targaryen\" title=\"Aerion Targaryen\">Aerion Targaryen</a> is sent to <a href=\"/index.php/Lys\" title=\"Lys\">Lys</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rthk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rthk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_V_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon V Targaryen\">Aegon Targaryen</a> joins the hedge knight Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Duncan_the_Tall\" title=\"Duncan the Tall\">Duncan the Tall</a> as his squire.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rthk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rthk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>The <a href=\"/index.php/Great_Spring_Sickness\" title=\"Great Spring Sickness\">Great Spring Sickness</a> begins and spreads.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragotappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragotappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Aerys_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Aerys I Targaryen\">Aerys Targaryen</a> is crowned as King Aerys I Targaryen upon the death of King Daeron II. His wife, Princess <a href=\"/index.php/Aelinor_Penrose\" title=\"Aelinor Penrose\">Aelinor Penrose</a>, becomes Queen.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_targaryen_kings:_aerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_targaryen_kings:_aerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Brynden_Rivers\" title=\"Brynden Rivers\">Brynden Rivers</a> is named <a href=\"/index.php/Hand_of_the_King\" title=\"Hand of the King\">Hand of the King</a> for King <a href=\"/index.php/Aerys_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Aerys I Targaryen\">Aerys I Targaryen</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_targaryen_kings:_aerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_targaryen_kings:_aerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Births\">Births</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=209_AC&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Births\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Cerelle_Lannister_(daughter_of_Tybolt)\" title=\"Cerelle Lannister (daughter of Tybolt)\">Cerelle Lannister</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Deaths\">Deaths</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=209_AC&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Deaths\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Arlan_of_Pennytree\" title=\"Arlan of Pennytree\">Arlan of Pennytree</a>, of a chill.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rthk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rthk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Baelor_Targaryen_(son_of_Daeron_II)\" title=\"Baelor Targaryen (son of Daeron II)\">Baelor Targaryen</a>, slain by his brother Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Maekar_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Maekar I Targaryen\">Maekar</a>, due to a <a href=\"/index.php/Tourney\" title=\"Tourney\">tourney</a> mishap.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rthk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rthk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Humfrey_Beesbury\" title=\"Humfrey Beesbury\">Humfrey Beesbury</a>, slain during the <a href=\"/index.php/Trial_of_Seven\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Trial of Seven\">Trial of Seven</a> by Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Donnel_of_Duskendale\" title=\"Donnel of Duskendale\">Donnel of Duskendale</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rthk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rthk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Humfrey_Hardyng\" title=\"Humfrey Hardyng\">Humfrey Hardyng</a>, severely wounded during the Trial of Seven, later succumbed of his wounds.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rthk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-7\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rthk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Valarr_Targaryen\" title=\"Valarr Targaryen\">Valarr Targaryen</a>, due to the Great Spring Sickness, mere hours before his grandfather, King Daeron II.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Matarys_Targaryen\" title=\"Matarys Targaryen\">Matarys Targaryen</a>, due to the Great Spring Sickness, mere hours before his grandfather, King Daeron II.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>King <a href=\"/index.php/Daeron_II_Targaryen\" title=\"Daeron II Targaryen\">Daeron II Targaryen</a>, due to the Great Spring Sickness.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&